:::Torca:::

Torca: Well, when i was new, i was treated very poorly.  Liono Prime was the 
leader, and he was pretty much a terrible leader(his opinion).  I was once 
captured by this guy Onyx Primal, and i nearly got my mechfluid sucked 
because of how slow it took Liono.  As the war progressed, things got better. 
I got a home in the CF, proved myself as a warrior, and made some friends. 
But Iron Raptor is really only a small step up from Liono(again, his 
opinion). So i guess another faction would be right up my alley.  But what 
faction?

--part1_97.15957d4a.2838b2e9_boundary
